bibl.title: Some Thoughts on the Procuratorship Alexandriae Pelusi Paraetoni.
bibl.note: Based on a Master's dissertation at the Classics Faculty of Oxford, 2008. Interpretation of the procuratorship Alexandriae Pelusi Paraetoni attested in an inscription from Ostia found in Rome, C.I.L. XIV, 170 = VI, 1624.
